(5, ' Fashion needs to step up as UK is ‘in a paralysis’, says Jonathan Anderson', 'fashion-needs-to-step-up-as-uk-is-in-a-paralysis-says-jonathan-anderson.png', '<p id=\"isPasted\" style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.5; font-family: GuardianTextEgyptian, \"Guardian Text Egyptian Web\", Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; --source-text-decoration-thickness:2px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>British fashion needs &ldquo;to step up and say something&rdquo; at a moment when the country is &ldquo;in a paralysis&rdquo;, the leading&nbsp;<a data-component=\"auto-linked-tag\" data-link-name=\"in body link\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/fashion/london-fashion-week\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(187, 59, 128);\">London fashion week</a> designer Jonathan Anderson has said.</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.5; font-family: GuardianTextEgyptian, \"Guardian Text Egyptian Web\", Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; --source-text-decoration-thickness:2px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>His JW Anderson show on Sunday will revive the punk-spirit stagewear of the dancer and choreographer Michael Clark &ndash; labelled &ldquo;the David Bowie of dance&rdquo; &ndash; in a catwalk show celebrating the anti-establishment heritage of British culture.</p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: Sylfaen; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><br></div><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.5; font-family: GuardianTextEgyptian, \"Guardian Text Egyptian Web\", Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; --source-text-decoration-thickness:2px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>Rebellion is in the air as London fashion week begins. The entire week of shows are dedicated to the memory of&nbsp;<a data-link-name=\"in body link\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/fashion/2022/dec/30/dame-vivienne-westwood-obituary\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(187, 59, 128);\">Dame Vivienne Westwood, who died in December</a>. The Design Museum has just announced a major exhibition entitled Rebel &ndash; 30 Years of London Fashion to open in September, sponsored by Alexander McQueen.</p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: Sylfaen; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: center; display: flex; -webkit-box-pack: center; justify-content: center; background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); color: rgb(18, 18, 18); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><br></div><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.5; font-family: GuardianTextEgyptian, \"Guardian Text Egyptian Web\", Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; --source-text-decoration-thickness:2px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>&ldquo;I also work in France, where rebellion means a strike,&rdquo; said Anderson, who has catapulted the bourgeois Spanish leather goods house of Loewe into a Paris fashion week hot ticket, where clothes are decorated with acrylic egg shells or deflated balloons, and the front row has featured Zadie Smith and Timoth&eacute;e Chalamet. &ldquo;But in Britain, rebellion has also this crazy, creative, vibrant artistic identity &ndash; from Clark and McQueen, to Leigh Bowery, Tracey Emin. Westwood was extraordinary &ndash; she changed British culture, and it feels like it is only now that we are appreciating the full scale of what she did.&rdquo;</p><p style=\'box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.5; font-family: GuardianTextEgyptian, \"Guardian Text Egyptian Web\", Georgia, serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; --source-text-decoration-thickness:2px; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\'>London fashion week is depleted of major names, with Victoria Beckham having joined the Alexander McQueen and Stella McCartney labels on the Paris schedule. Anderson, who created the pregnancy-announcing boilersuit for&nbsp;<a data-link-name=\"in body link\" href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2023/feb/13/rihanna-super-bowl-performance-greatest-pregnancy-reveal\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-top-style: initial; border-right-style: initial; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: initial; border-top-color: initial; border-right-color: initial; border-bottom-color: rgb(220, 220, 220); border-left-color: initial; border-image: initial; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(187, 59, 128);\">Rihanna&rsquo;s Super Bowl half-time show</a> that made front pages all over the world &ndash; a derogatory tweet from Donald Trump was the icing on the cake of global publicity &ndash; has serious clout in the industry. But keeping his eponymous brand in London has required &ldquo;soul-searching&rdquo;, Anderson says.</p><figure data-spacefinder-role=\"inline\" data-spacefinder-type=\"model.dotcomrendering.pageElements.ImageBlockElement\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: common-ligatures; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 400; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: medium; line-height: inherit; font-family: Sylfaen; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; color: rgb(18, 18, 18); letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative;\"><source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/a6839f1cbfda437971a564894e8ff9128ba28b73/0_150_4512_2707/master/4512.jpg?width=620&quality=45&dpr=2&s=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 660px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;<source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/a6839f1cbfda437971a564894e8ff9128ba28b73/0_150_4512_2707/master/4512.jpg?width=620&quality=85&dpr=1&s=none\" media=\"(min-width: 660px)\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;<source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/a6839f1cbfda437971a564894e8ff9128ba28b73/0_150_4512_2707/master/4512.jpg?width=605&quality=45&dpr=2&s=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 480px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;<source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/a6839f1cbfda437971a564894e8ff9128ba28b73/0_150_4512_2707/master/4512.jpg?width=605&quality=85&dpr=1&s=none\" media=\"(min-width: 480px)\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;<source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/a6839f1cbfda437971a564894e8ff9128ba28b73/0_150_4512_2707/master/4512.jpg?width=445&quality=45&dpr=2&s=none\" media=\"(min-width: 320px) and (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 1.25), (min-width: 320px) and (min-resolution: 120dpi)\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;<source srcset=\"https://i.guim.co.